### Loan Application — LoanApplicationAgent
### POST /api/loan/apply
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Excellent credit: strong applicant → auto APPROVED path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loan/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "APP-2001",
  "fullName": "Julia Meier",
  "requestedAmount": 25000.00,
  "annualIncome": 95000.00,
  "employmentStatus": "Permanent full-time",
  "creditScore": 780,
  "existingMonthlyDebt": 450.00,
  "loanTermMonths": 48,
  "loanPurpose": "Home renovation"
}

###

### Very poor credit: high debt, unstable income → auto REJECTED path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loan/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "APP-2002",
  "fullName": "Kevin Müller",
  "requestedAmount": 40000.00,
  "annualIncome": 28000.00,
  "employmentStatus": "Part-time, contract",
  "creditScore": 420,
  "existingMonthlyDebt": 1800.00,
  "loanTermMonths": 60,
  "loanPurpose": "Debt consolidation"
}

###

### Fair credit: borderline case → underwriting path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loan/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "APP-2003",
  "fullName": "Carla Rossi",
  "requestedAmount": 15000.00,
  "annualIncome": 52000.00,
  "employmentStatus": "Permanent full-time",
  "creditScore": 620,
  "existingMonthlyDebt": 900.00,
  "loanTermMonths": 36,
  "loanPurpose": "Education"
}
